  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0bb0\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Family members tragically lost their lives in Vavuniya train accident",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "A family member tragically died in a train accident in Vavuniya Chettikulam area today.",
        "The accident occurred today (04) afternoon when the train from Colombo to Thalaimannar was traveling in Vavuniya Chettikulam area.",
        "The family member who was injured in the accident was immediately rescued and admitted to the Chettikulam Divisional Hospital, but he died without treatment.",
        "A 33-year-old family member named Ruksan from Gandhinagar area died in the incident. It is to be noted that he is the Chettikulam Regional Coordinator of the Tamil Eelam Liberation Movement (SIRRELO).",
        "It is noteworthy that the train continued its journey only after a delay of a few hours due to the accident."
      ],
